      "message": "Patch Set 5: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/221555f0-2d3a-11e2-9af4-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
